=== Sample Size Justification

With n=200 and 12 assessment points over 3 years (2,400 observations):
    - 80% power to detect linear association between infection count and Bell scale decline (regression $beta$=1.5 points per infection, SD=10) at $alpha$=0.05
    - Adequate power for subgroup comparisons (n $gt.eq$50 per treatment timing category)


